Package it.polimi.ingsw.client.gui.utils

Class GUISwitcher

java.lang.Object
it.polimi.ingsw.client.gui.utils.GUISwitcher
public class GUISwitcher
extends java.lang.Object
Singleton used to control active scene-controller, and easily switch between them. It's also used as a container for controller's instances.
